				\begin{document}$$\Delta E = \sqrt {\left( {L_{1}^{*} - L_{2}^{*} } \right)^{2} + \left( {a_{1}^{*} - a_{2}^{*} } \right)^{2} + \left( {b_{1}^{*} - b_{2}^{*} } \right)^{2} }$$\end{document}ΔE=L1∗-L2∗2+a1∗-a2∗2+b1∗-b2∗2
2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
