The Arrhenius Eq. (3), activation energy value, reaction rate constant and Eqs. (4), (5) and (6) were used to prepare kinetic models of changes in the quality parameters during storage. The function of the quality of the zero-order reaction can be expressed as follows:7\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
